otc.tokens.tip:
Notes and Tips:


Application: For mainstream token OTC sharing opening, please contact our BD, it can be opened after signing the cooperation agreement.

Operation: OTC merchants/customers are all online 24 hours a day, which requires your customer service team to be on duty 24/7 and provide a common mobile phone on duty to ensure that our customer service can quickly contact the person in charge of your company in case of complaint orders.


24-hour Duty Tips:


General advice on duty cycle in 8 hour, ensure 24 hours online processing, if the current resource constraints/operation cannot support 24 hours on duty, our proposal will be temporarily closed OTC sharing until service team online.

Risk control: Recently there have been more OTC orders and more frozen bank CARDS of platform merchants. Therefore, after opening OTC sharing for you, please be more strict with platform users.


Tips:


High-risk areas (by eye identification) : Chongqing, Guangdong, Zhejiang and Hainan provinces and cities are the concentrated areas where we have found money laundering. The general advice is that if users were born after 1998, (holding a photo of ID card), you should pay more attention.

24 hour withdrawal limit :(this limit applies to open sharing only)

The logic of the withdrawal limit we set is that system will calculates the withdrawal price in real time to make sure that the assets in the account are at least equivalent to the USDT purchased over the bought amount thought OTC if withdrawal triggered within 24 hours.

Like if user now has USDT, BTC and a range of other assets, we do a real-time calculation to make sure that the assets in the account are greater than or equal to the USDT purchased over the OTC (i.e. 100USDT), and extra token beyond 100USDT can be withdrawn.
